<br>
Hide of course is a bit differant, and there are mobs of all sorts that potentially can see through. Sometimes you can waltz right past a Froglok Jin Wizard in Seb, and sometimes it goes off like a blue burn monkey casting Force Shock on you. Bats in Guk and Sol B will see Hide, but if your behind them and sneaking they will not notice you. Bats in Maidens Eye will never see you, but Vampires such as Coterie Legionaire's will always see you. A true list of mobs can be created that can see through rogue Hide, but care must be made that we do no confuse Sneak with it. Although the two abilities are used together, they definitly have differant effects on how a mob can perceive us depending on facing and orientation, level vs mob level, etc.<br>
<br>
Enix Dreadraven, Assassin of Royal Norrathian Guard<br>
